OL,3,CBristol mother died after tripping on
OL,4,C'metal flap' outside hospital
OL,6,FA mother-of-two died three weeks after
OL,7,Ftripping on a metal flap outside a
OL,8,Fhospital, an inquest has heard.
OL,10,FLorna Loxton, a former auxiliary nurse
OL,11,Ffrom Wells, had been at Bristol Heart
OL,12,FInstitute for a cardiology appointment
OL,13,Fon January 7, 2025.
OL,15,FShe fell walking to her taxi outside
OL,16,Fthe hospital when her wheeled walking
OL,17,Fframe struck a metal flap covering a
OL,18,Fbollard.
