OL,3,CBristol mother died after tripping on
OL,4,C'metal flap' outside hospital
OL,6,FThe 55-year-old tripped, breaking her
OL,7,Fhip and hitting her head on the
OL,8,Fground. She underwent surgery on the
OL,9,Fhip but her condition deteriorated and
OL,10,Fshe died in hospital on January 28.
OL,12,FMs Loxton's daughter Danni and son
OL,13,FMark have paid tribute to their mother
OL,14,Fwho lived with myotonic dystrophy,
OL,15,Fwhich causes muscle weakness.
OL,17,FShe was described as an animal lover,
OL,18,Fwho enjoyed riding and caring for
OL,19,Fhorses, as well as looking after her
OL,20,Fthree dogs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
