OL,3,CBristol mother died after tripping on
OL,4,C'metal flap' outside hospital
OL,6,FDanni described her mother as an
OL,7,Famazing person who "overcame so much
OL,8,Fto live the independent life she
OL,9,Fwanted".
OL,11,F"We are devastated that mum suffered
OL,12,Fthe indignity of falling as she left
OL,13,Fthe hospital, over what the NHS Trust
OL,14,Fthemselves described as a "trip
OL,15,Fhazard", and they also admitted the
OL,16,Farea had not been subject to a health
OL,17,Fand safety risk assessment.
OL,19,F"This is not good enough and is not in
OL,20,Fthe best interests of any patients,
OL,21,Fvisitors or staff."
