OL,3,CBristol mother died after tripping on
OL,4,C'metal flap' outside hospital
OL,6,FGiving evidence, ward sister Nia
OL,7,FShellard, who was first on the scene
OL,8,Fwith a colleague, said Lorna lost
OL,9,Fconsciousness and was bleeding from
OL,10,Fher head.
OL,12,F"She was thrown to the ground (after)
OL,13,FI saw her strike something," said Ms
OL,14,FShellard. "I saw metal sticking out
OL,15,Fand it made most sense that is what
OL,16,Fshe hit. I didn't see her lose control
OL,17,Fof the walker."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
