OL,3,CBristol mother died after tripping on
OL,4,C'metal flap' outside hospital
OL,6,FShe agreed in a later report, the
OL,7,Fnurse believed the protruding metal
OL,8,Fwas 'something to sort urgently'. "I
OL,9,Fwas concerned about it," she added.
OL,11,FGriff Griffiths, Deputy Director of
OL,12,FEstates & Facilities for the
OL,13,FUniversity Hospitals Bristol and
OL,14,FWeston, admitted his department was
OL,15,Funaware the bollard wasn't secured at
OL,16,Fthe time of Lorna's fall and no risk
OL,17,Fassessment was in place.
OL,19,F"The bollard wasn't secured to the
OL,20,Fflange by a bolt or padlock, I don't
OL,21,Fknow for long," he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
