OL,3,CBristol mother died after tripping on
OL,4,C'metal flap' outside hospital
OL,6,F"There is a risk in operating but the
OL,7,Fmortality rate if we don't is up to
OL,8,F90%," he added. "The longer you wait,
OL,9,Fthe more likely you are to develop
OL,10,Fproblems."
OL,12,FConsultant Daniel Freshwater-Turner
OL,13,Fadded Lorna was frail due to her
OL,14,F'chronic conditions' and that she
OL,15,Fdeteriorated quickly after the
OL,16,Foperation. "Colleagues would have
OL,17,Fthought the prognosis was not good,"
OL,18,Fhe said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
