OL,6,F"Due to the nature of her conditions,
OL,7,Fthe odds were stacked against her.
OL,8,FThat's the biggest contributory factor
OL,9,Fbut the trigger event was the fall."
OL,11,FLorna's family agreed to withdraw life
OL,12,Fsupport and her kidneys were donated.
OL,14,FIn a statement, University Hospitals
OL,15,FBristol and Weston NHS Foundation
OL,16,FTrust said: "We would like to offer
OL,17,Four heartfelt condolences to Lorna's
OL,18,Ffamily.
